ut there went up a mist from the earth, and watered the whole face of the ground.","year":-4004},{"id":"rec3uiE442eAxz8UN","ref":"Gen.2.7","text":"And the LORD God formed man of the dust of the ground, and breathed into his nostrils the breath of life; and man became a living soul.","year":-4004},{"id":"recmb6LrwBeHu6MJK","ref":"Gen.2.8","text":"And the LORD God planted a garden eastward in Eden; and there he put the man whom he had formed.","year":-4004}]}
